 	<li>If you choose to use Elevate Online Marketing Ltd. to upload your privacy policy, general website terms or any other terms we would always recommend having these independently checked by a professional legal representative. Our terms cater for most websites and are considered general usage terms. We can offer a bespoke service if you require the terms to be checked by a legal professional.</li>
 	<li>The privacy policy, general website terms or any other terms that we offer clients will be produced by a third party.</li>
