 	<li class="x_MsoNormal">WebCare packages that include WebAssist afford the client up to 20 minutes of updates to the site per calendar month. Updates are limited to text/image based changes on a per request basis. Requests for changes to site coding or changes that exceed the work included in WebAssist are subject to charge.</li>
