<h4 class="has-text-align-center">Retrieve abandoned carts with a personalised message and “one-time “offers</h4>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Sales naturally fall through the cracks, and a high cart abandonment rate is quite common for online retailers during Black Friday events. Optimising and recovering abandoned carts&nbsp;is and must for any eCommerce business not just during seasonal periods but as a normal part of your marketing strategy.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Creating a customer remarketing campaign can increase the chances of getting customers back to your site and completing the sales journey. Retargeting your visitors with a paid ad campaign allows you to bring them back to your store and back to the point of sale.</p>
